ue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ihl1665702775639.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ihl1665702775639.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ihl1665702775639.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ihl1665702775639\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Defines the behavior of the worksheet plug-in component when the main development\n    object being edited is renamed.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ihl1665702775639_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__codeblock_mgr_xsm_mzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ws_objectRenamed\nparams\n string pObjectUrl : IN\nendparams\n   \n; &lt;... Your code here ...&gt;\nend; operation ws_objectRenamed </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__section_ij3_ysm_mzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d721432e54\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__p_d4673e1_d4674e1_d4675e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">pObjectUrl</span> —new name of the current main development object.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__section_rwc_zsm_mzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d721432e66\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__p_d4679e1_d4680e1_d4681e1\">The Uniface IDE activates this operation to notify the\n        worksheet plug-in that the current main development object has been renamed. Depending on\n        the worksheet, this may have some impact, so this operation enables you to respond\n        appropriately.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__p_d4682e1_d4683e1_d4684e1\">The operation is optional.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__section_djy_mhr_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d721432e78\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__p_d4688e1_d4689e1_d4690e1\">The following operation sends a message to the Messages tab\n        by calling the IDE API operation <span class=\"keyword apiname\">outputMessage</span> and it resets the value of\n        a component variable ($URL$) and field (URL.ENT).</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ihl1665702775639_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ihl1665702775639__codeblock_wdm_ctm_mzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ws_objectRenamed\n params\n string pObjectUrl : IN\n endparams\n activate \"IDE_API_1\".outputMessage(\"Main Object renamed (Url=%%pObjectUrl).\")\n if ($procerror != 0)\n putmess \"Activate error: %%$procerror%%%, %%$procerrorcontext%%%\"\n endif\n $URL$ = pObjectUrl\n URL.ENT = $URL$\n show\nend ; ws_objectRenamed</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ws_objectRenamed Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Defines the behavior of the worksheet plug-in component when the main development object being edited is renamed. Explain this code operation ws_objectRenamed params string pObjectUrl : IN endparams ; <... Your code here ...> end; operation ws_objectRenamed Copy Parameters pObjectUrl —new name of the current main development object. Description The Uniface IDE activates this operation to notify the worksheet plug-in that the current main development object has been renamed. Depending on the worksheet, this may have some impact, so this operation enables you to respond appropriately. The operation is optional. Example The following operation sends a message to the Messages tab by calling the IDE API operation outputMessage and it resets the value of a component variable ($URL$) and field (URL.ENT). Explain this code operation ws_objectRenamed params string pObjectUrl : IN endparams activate \"IDE_API_1\".outputMessage(\"Main Object renamed (Url=%%pObjectUrl).\") if ($procerror != 0) putmess \"Activate error: %%$procerror%%%, %%$procerrorcontext%%%\" endif $URL$ = pObjectUrl URL.ENT = $URL$ show end ; ws_objectRenamed Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}